710858f-a.text:

710859f-b.title: Manhattan: 3rd Street - Avenue B
710859f-b.text:
East 3rd Street, north side, west from, but not including Ave. B.
A1so shown, is the Most Holy Redeemer R.C. Church, at Nos. 161-165, east of
Ave. A.. conducted by the Redemptorist Fathers of N.Y.
Ausust 26, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
2w 3rd St. east of Ave. A. Polish church. Neg. A-85
June 25, 1941
